text: A Nnbi! Mara tebrum i tlawin, brut asent mara taaddi tallit n tarda nnsent. Eesbet tallit. Eezzbet i Oebbi, Mass nnwen. Ur tent ssuffu$et si texxamin nnsent, ur d teff$ent, siwa ma, s tidep, ccvent. D tigi ay d tilisa n Oebbi. Win izegren tilisa n Oebbi, ni$ idens imanis.
